{"tid":714994,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"去IKEA食野","createTime":"2018-06-24T06:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T12:10:33.000Z","uid":85524,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1f2b6d34517eec51bcd5d223974934e9d73a1a77","tid":714994,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T06:02:44.000Z","msg":"去親IKEA食野， 次次都爆哂膨。<br />\n頭先自己一個去食， 買完野食拎住周圍走， 冇位坐。 <br />\n<br />\n等左我諗15 分鐘， 突然有個好心人走埋黎同我講佢果邊有位。 果一刻覺得香港仲有好人。 跟住有個人問我旁有冇人， 我話冇， 比佢用。人感染人係真的， 對身邊人好d,  果個人又會將哩份大愛繼續傳開去， 社會多和諧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以後都唔會再去IKEA食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9364c08c87af1e2769c55b0bce5290304e9f801a","tid":714994,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T06:03:58.000Z","msg":"一個人食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e740cc1e1fce766dc240d40bb1cb860dd5a70ff3","tid":714994,"uid":75448,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T06:06:14.000Z","msg":"一個人就企吧枱食啦"},{"pid":"3ffbb2f466803bda4682455f59960fffdc9cb721","tid":714994,"uid":87043,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T06:10:46.000Z","msg":"一個人take away 啦"},{"pid":"685f5f78e88cd7ab133a7b77537c80350faf630a","tid":714994,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T06:13:42.000Z","msg":"一個人去企枱食囉"},{"pid":"6cd2c51ab227461b23c2e95360260b11a313d17b","tid":714994,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e740cc1e1fce766dc240d40bb1cb860dd5a70ff3","tid":714994,"uid":75448,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T06:06:14.000Z","msg":"一個人就企吧枱食啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T06:24:02.000Z","msg":"讓位比我果個就係企吧， 本身連企吧都爆埋"},{"pid":"39cdb6ce06cb0fceb334650a168cfa32337ac3a8","tid":714994,"uid":1188,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"cit